title: Konami Is WORSE Than I Thought...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the release of the Metal Gear Master Collection. This release should have been great but instead serves as a reminder of the current state of Konami. Incredibly greedy and exponentially lazy. Thanks for watching!
